# Commit Message Convention

# Type:  feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore, perf, ci, build, revert
# Scope: (optional) module or component name
# Subject: imperative mood, max 50 chars, no period
#
# Body:  detailed explanation, wrap at 72 chars
# Footer:  references to issues, breaking changes

# Example:
# feat(auth): add JWT token refresh endpoint
#
# Added refresh token endpoint to improve authentication flow.
# Fixes #123
# BREAKING CHANGE: old token format no longer supported